          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (sandbox) (rate(azureclaw_agt_policy_evaluations_total{decision=\"deny\",sandbox=~\"$sandbox\"}[1h])) / clamp_min(sum by (sandbox) (rate(azureclaw_agt_policy_evaluations_total{sandbox=~\"$sandbox\"}[1h])), 1e-9))",
